，联合项目预计将在周四举行的<a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3219775/chinas-xi-jinping-chair-cc5-summit-central-asian-heads-state-may-18?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220788_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="2d8a3741-7261-4d0e-886c-bd05c26057c3" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">区域峰会</a>上提上议程。</p><p>中国国家主席习近平及其来自哈萨克斯坦、吉尔吉斯斯坦、塔吉克斯坦、土库曼斯坦和乌兹别克斯坦的国家主席将在中国西北部城市西安参加为期两天的中国-中亚峰会，此次峰会正值中国面临越来越大的美国脱钩压力之际-领导西部。 </p><div class="meter__linear relative" id="default-meter-page-views-11"><img width="auto" height="1" src="https://www.scmp.com/images/1x1.png" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="dm__l3"><hr class="vertical-line"><div class="dm__lw"><svg class="dm__l" height="24" viewBox="0 0 18 24" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g style="stroke:#000;fill:none;fill-rule:evenodd;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5"><rect height="13.5" rx="1.5" width="16.5" x=".75" y="9.75"></rect><path d="m3.75 9.75v-3.75c0-2.89949494 2.35050506-5.25 5.25-5.25 2.8994949 0 5.25 2.35050506 5.25 5.25v3.75"></path><path d="m9.00000067 15.75c-.20710745 0-.37500067.1678932-.37500067.3749993 0 .2071075.16789322.3750007.37500067.3750007.20710611 0 .37499933-.1678932.37499933-.3750007.0002665-.0995369-.03915673-.1950746-.10954072-.2654586-.070384-.070384-.16592164-.1098072-.26545861-.1095407z"></path></g></svg></div></div><div class="dm__b center-block"><div><div class="dm__h mb-16">您已达到免费文章数量限制。</div><div class="dm__t center-block">订阅 SCMP 以无限制地访问我们屡获殊荣的新闻</div><div class="dm__s2 mt-30"><div class="dm__sb" id="subscribe-btn-11-large" role="button" tabindex="0" subscriptions-action="subscribe" subscriptions-service="subscribe.google.com" subscriptions-display="true" subscriptions-decorate="">订阅</div><div class="dm__m"><span>或</span><a href="https://subscribe.scmp.com/">探索我们的计划</a></div></div></div><div subscriptions-actions="" subscriptions-display="NOT data.loggedIn" cla