-data-missed-forecasts?utm_source=rss_feed</guid><link/> https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3220801/wall-street-banks-are-split-chinas-growth-prospects-after-aprils-data-missed-forecasts?utm_source=rss_feed<author><![CDATA[Bloomberg]]></author><category>商业</category><category>中国股市</category><category>香港股市</category><category>股票</category><category>在美国上市的中国股票</category><category>中国经济</category><category>在 4 月份的数据低于预期后，华尔街银行对中国的增长前景存在分歧</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Will Biden’s ‘little Nato’ G7 unity push cause an ‘economic iron curtain’ to fall over US-China relations?]]></title><description><![CDATA[<p>分析人士称，预计美国总统<a href="https://www.scmp.com/knowledge/people/joe-biden/news" title="">拜登</a>将在访问亚太地区期间强调<a href="https://www.scmp.com/topics/g7?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220760_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="1ca67c6a-452e-4b3f-8e19-7fdb91c35cd3" data-entity-type="taxonomy_term" data-entity-bundle="topics">七国集团</a>国家之间的团结，并强调华盛顿在与<a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/china" title="" data-entity-uuid="08925cfe-01ce-4932-b9e2-be5b255efe63" data-entity-type="taxonomy_term" data-entity-bundle="section">中国</a>的紧张局势升级以及<a href="https://www.scmp.com/topics/ukraine-war?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220760_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="afbfaf37-bf7c-478a-8eee-1c796d3b4437" data-entity-type="taxonomy_term" data-entity-bundle="topics">乌克兰持续不断的冲突中</a>对该地区的贡献。</p><p>拜登将于本周五在<a href="https://www.scmp.com/topics/japan?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3220760_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="73990659-b9b2-48a9-b582-fdf28ced9714" data-entity-type="taxonomy_term" data-entity-bundle="topics">日本</a>广岛参加七国集团峰会，届时他将加深与长期盟友的关系。他当时计划作为第一位<a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/australasia/article/3218513/joe-biden-make-landmark-visit-papua-new-guinea-us-vies-china-asia-pacific-influence?utm_source=goog